{"tid":1479771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對於popo要非法入侵私人地方，請大家依照堡壘準則作適合自衛","createTime":"2019-08-17T04:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T08:35:21.000Z","uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7780cfe2891891e2951950b5a5cfd6eb05538c3","tid":1479771,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:41:11.000Z","msg":"城堡準則（英語：castle doctrine，又譯為堡壘原則），亦稱城堡法（castle law）或居所防禦法（defense of habitation law）；居住防衛權，一種法律原則，始於羅馬法，存在於英美法中，賦予在特定情況下，被侵犯人可以對於入侵其宅邸（在某些州，也可以是機動車或工作場所等合法佔用的空間）的進犯者使用武力（甚至是致命武力）進行防範和對抗的權力，而對於所造成的後果免於法律責任且不被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9F%8E%E5%A0%A1%E5%87%86%E5%88%99?wprov=sfti1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25A0%25A1%25E5%2587%2586%25E5%2588%2599%3Fwprov%3Dsfti1&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75VSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=0fba335c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9F%8E%E5%A0%A1%E5%87%86%E5%88%99?wprov=sfti1</a>"},{"pid":"2ed208897b50baf3f3a4fd7b0a9e7fc0c1e0669a","tid":1479771,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T04:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d868f0a7febeaf0d0732dcdb009adc511b9b97","tid":1479771,"uid":174084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1678608719047846/photos/a.1764177917157592/2380163225559055/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1678608719047846%2Fphotos%2Fa.1764177917157592%2F2380163225559055%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75VSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=8d9905fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1678608719047846/photos/a.1764177917157592/2380163225559055/?type=3&amp;theater</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZypF6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/